The repo contains few usefull PowerShell scripts.
If you don't want to use the script, you could check another repository which contains only functions (https://github.com/FutureIsHere/PowerShell-Functions)

1. Get-DiskStatus - checks health status of disk volumes using "diskpart" and creates an event in the EventLog. 
	It was created mainly to monitor a soft RAID volumes failures in Windows 7.
2. Fix-FailedVolume - initiates disk volume recovery process (using "diskpart") utility.